<br />
I though that a spellsword type class would be rather interesting.. A class that wouldbe able to imbue their weapon with a proc (something along the lines of the "call of" line that rangers get). They would probably be an INT caster hybrid, possibly sustaining a slight mana drain per proc, to keep their damage output in balance. Armor would probably be light - chain at most. Other spells they would be capable of using would possibly be INT caster self buffs, such as the shielding line ormaybe some self runes or hastes, and possibly some magic based slow spells, based off those of the enchanter.
<br />

<br />
Its a far fetched idea, but I thought it would be cool to have an interesting INT based class out there to have fun with.
